  "title": "BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p><p></p><p>The Business Development Manager is responsible for expanding the company’s mobile retail and service operations by identifying new business opportunities, improving sales channels, and forming strategic partnerships with distributors, brands, and online platforms. The role requires strong market analysis, negotiation skills, and the ability to drive revenue growth.</p><p></p><p>Key Responsibilities</p><p></p><p>Develop business strategies to increase sales for mobile phones, accessories, and repair services</p><p></p><p>Identify and secure partnerships with distributors, wholesalers, and mobile brands (Samsung, Apple, Xiaomi, etc.)</p><p></p><p>Expand online sales channels: Shopee, Lazada, TikTok Shop</p><p></p><p>Introduce new product lines and improve service offerings</p><p></p><p>Analyse market trends and competitors to recommend pricing strategies</p><p></p><p>Drive promotional campaigns and customer acquisition programs</p><p></p><p>Maintain strong relationships with suppliers and corporate clients</p><p></p><p>Monitor sales performance and prepare monthly business reports</p><p></p><p>Support management in planning store expansion</p><p></p><p>Requirements</p><p></p><p>MBA or equivalent degree in Business / Marketing / Management</p><p></p><p>3–5 years experience in mobile retail, telecom, or consumer electronics</p><p></p><p>Strong negotiation and communication skills</p><p></p><p>Knowledge of Singapore’s retail and e-commerce market</p><p></p><p>Ability to work independently and achieve revenue targets</p>",
